query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q tq s) */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 5
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('amd',
'constexpr',
'continuous-deployment',
'environment',
'facebook-opengraph',
'hardware',
'laravel-5.7',
'lme4',
'nav',
'railstutorial.org',
'swiftmailer',
'wso2carbon',
'xlsx',
'yui');
